Information

Developer: Games Krasnov Craft

Description
The story of the pixel-hero who fights evil in the game Pixlgun 3D - Survival Shooter. Welcome to a world built of blocks, and that is crawling with zombies and other enemies. Over time, the number of zombies and enemies increases, and then around you are whole hordes! So it will not relax. The game has several weapons such as shotgun, Uzi and a pistol, as well as 6 large cards.

Installation
1. Install the apk.
2. Play.
3. Seed & enjoy!
